<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No, it&apos;s high science fiction, no romance. &quot;Explicit&quot; and what someone would recommend to a teen is entirely relative to the person you are asking. <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No, it's high science fiction, no romance. "Explicit" and what someone would recommend to a teen is entirely relative to the person you are asking. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
