<span id="freeTextContainer10346660404493474817">The writing was drier than a cracker in the desert...<br/><br/>But I loved the book anyway! <br/><br/>It definitely reads like a scientific/army report but this was such an interesting twist on the classic sci-fi (first contact?). I only recommend it if you already love sci-fi and diseases apocalyptic books.<br/><br/>Left me wanting more... I&apos;ll definitely read more from the author!</span>
  <span id="freeText10346660404493474817" style="display:none">The writing was drier than a cracker in the desert...<br /><br />But I loved the book anyway! <br /><br />It definitely reads like a scientific/army report but this was such an interesting twist on the classic sci-fi (first contact?). I only recommend it if you already love sci-fi and diseases apocalyptic books.<br /><br />Left me wanting more... I'll definitely read more from the author!</span>
