    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_1715471896" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1715471896" />
    <a title="Lauren Stoolfire" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6857324-lauren-stoolfire"><img alt="Lauren Stoolfire" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1595823149p2/6857324.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1715471896?book_show_action=true">Apr 08, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lauren Stoolfire" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lauren Stoolfire" href="/user/show/6857324-lauren-stoolfire">Lauren Stoolfire</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780394415253" href="/book/show/1331973.The_Andromeda_Strain">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6857324-lauren-stoolfire?shelf=sci-fi">sci-fi</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1715471896" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11956566878802830618">I had high expectations for <i>The Andromeda Strain</i> by Michael Crichton. He&apos;s written some of my favorite books, and some of my favorite movies as well. Unfortunately, I wasn&apos;t as nearly as invested in this as I was hoping to be. The book has no excuse being this boring. I guess I was expecting more of a thriller.</span>
  <span id="freeText11956566878802830618" style="display:none">I had high expectations for <i>The Andromeda Strain</i> by Michael Crichton. He's written some of my favorite books, and some of my favorite movies as well. Unfortunately, I wasn't as nearly as invested in this as I was hoping to be. The book has no excuse being this boring. I guess I was expecting more of a thriller.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11956566878802830618" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


