<li class='cover' id='bookCover_112537'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/112537.Rendezvous_with_Rama"><img alt="Rendezvous with Rama (Rama, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1405456427l/112537._SY160_.jpg" />
